<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="beside-prep">beside <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'saɪd/    美 /bɪ'saɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在…旁边：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She sat beside me. 
她坐在我旁边。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-beside-the-point">(be) beside the point</h3>
<p>1.<strong>离题；与主题无关</strong>  </p></div>